===Etymology===
{{zh-ref|Smith (2011)}} groups {{och-l|孩|tr=*gəə}} "to toddle, to stand upright > child" along with these items:

*{{och-l|荄|tr=*kəə}}, & its derivative {{och-l|根|tr=*kəən}} "root", 
*{{och-l|核|tr=*grəək}} "germ, kernel", 
*{{och-l|骸|tr=grəə}} "(human) bones", 
*{{och-l|亥|tr=*gəəʔ}} "sprouting stage", i.e. "the moon’s first appearance" > "twelve earthly branch"

in the word-family "root, germ, generative core".

See {{och-l|核|tr=grəək}} for further etymology.

